542
00:46:08,000 --> 00:46:11,968
<font color="#ffff80">"...his rifle against my leg."</font>

543
00:46:12,033 --> 00:46:15,901
<font color="#ffff80">"behind him, Marcelos and Tomas lay dead."</font>

544
00:46:17,634 --> 00:46:22,334
