549
00:46:36,900 --> 00:46:38,968
<font color="#ffff80">"POW!</font>'
<i>[ bird screeching ]</i>

550
00:46:40,534 --> 00:46:42,467
<font color="#ffff80">"...and shot my leg off."</font>

551
00:46:42,534 --> 00:46:44,400
<font color="#ffff80"><i>[ child ]</i>  " He done the devils work."</font>

