556
00:47:00,234 --> 00:47:02,634
<i>[ another boy ]</i>
<font color="#ffff80">"...and take away our cattle and our goats."</font>

557
00:47:02,801 --> 00:47:04,834
<font color="#ffff80">"...and our land and our sheep."</font>

558
00:47:04,901 --> 00:47:08,634
<font color="#ffff80">but more terrible than losing all these things...</font>

559
00:47:08,701 --> 00:47:11,133
<font color="#ffff80">You will have lost your pride...</font>

