00:47:11,200 --> 00:47:13,133
<font color="#ffff80">...and your honor...</font>

561
00:47:13,200 --> 00:47:15,534
<font color="#ffff80">... and your dignity...</font>

562
00:47:15,601 --> 00:47:18,601
<font color="#ffff80">...and that you must never do...</font>

563
00:47:18,667 --> 00:47:20,601
<font color="#ffff80">...never!</font>

564
00:47:24,167 --> 00:47:27,067
 <i>[ children chattering and commenting ]</i>

