615
00:52:00,067 --> 00:52:02,501
All I ever wanted was to be part of this family.

616
00:52:02,567 --> 00:52:04,968
And now you are not a part of this family?

617
00:52:06,033 --> 00:52:09,067
<i>[ curses in spanish ]</i>

618
00:52:09,133 --> 00:52:11,701
<i>[ Don Braulio screams the alarm ]</i>      BARBAROSA!

619
00:52:11,768 --> 00:52:15,301
BARBAROSA!       BARBAROSA!

